results.name: ASICS Gel-Lyte III Sean Wotherspoon x atmos (PS)
results.story: Made for little kids, the Sean Wotherspoon x atmos x ASICS Gel Lyte 3 PS ‘Corduroy’ features a unique design celebrating the 30th anniversary of the retro silhouette and the 20th anniversary of the Japanese retailer. The corduroy upper is accented with interchangeable side stripes and removable logo patches. Mismatched colors between the right and left shoe draw a connection to Los Angeles and Tokyo, the respective homes of Sean Wotherspoon and atmos creative director Hirofumi Kojima.
